# 01 — Go Core & Concurrency

Ôn **Go core**, **concurrency**, **memory/GC** và **profiling** — bám CV (5k WebSocket, API 200%, memory footprint).

## Kiến thức cần cover

- **Goroutine & Scheduler:** M:N model, preemption, context switching; Netpoller (network I/O không block OS thread).
- **Memory:** Escape analysis, heap vs stack; liên hệ tối ưu API.
- **GC:** GOGC, tri-color mark and sweep; liên hệ WebSocket memory footprint.
- **Concurrency:** Channels (buffered/unbuffered), đóng channel an toàn; `sync` (WaitGroup, Mutex/RWMutex, Once, Pool); `context` (cancellation, timeout, deadline, values).
- **Patterns:** Worker pool, fan-out/fan-in, pipeline, errgroup.
- **Profiling:** `pprof` (CPU, heap), trace.

## Liên hệ CV

- "Engineered high-performance WebSocket server... 5,000 concurrent connections" → goroutine, netpoller, worker pool.
- "Boosting API performance by 200%" (BESSFU) → memory, GC, escape analysis.
- "WebSocket memory footprint" → GC tuning, sync.Pool.

